<plot>Derevenskiy detektiv (aka... Rural detective) is based on the eponymous book by Vil Lipatov. Detective Aniskin lives with his family in a rural village where people call him the "rural detective". Everyone in the village is respectful of Aniskin because of his wisdom and his good disposition. The villagers do not remember having any crime for many years. But one day an accordion is stolen from the manager of the local clubhouse. Detective Aniskin begins the investigation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?141140</url></doc>
